te-drive-time-pg-1-2-24-09-19-150x150.jpg\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a></span></h4>\r\n<h4 style=\"display: inline !important;\">Within walking distance to:</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Office</li>\r\n	<li>FarmersMarket</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<p style=\"display: inline !important;\">RenaissancePark</p>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<p style=\"display: inline !important;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"display: inline !important;\">Hotels</p>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<p style=\"display: inline !important;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"display: inline !important;\">GolfCourse</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4>Less than 10 minutes from:</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Interstate485</li>\r\n	<li>Interstate77</li>\r\n	<li>Interstate85</li>\r\n	<li>Charlotte Douglas International Airport</li>\r\n	<li>Light Rail Line</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>Less than 15 minutes from:</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>SouthPark</li>\r\n	<li>MyersPark</li>\r\n	<li>Uptown</li>\r\n	<li>LakeWylie</li>\r\n	<li>Dilworth / South End</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>U.S. National Whitewater Park</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\nAccess/traffic counts\r\n\r\nLoop\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.cms.k12.nc.us/Pages/Default.aspx\" target=\"_blank\">Schools</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://charmeck.org/mecklenburg/county/ParkandRec/Pages/default.aspx\" target=\"_blank\">Parks &amp; recreation links</a>\r\n\r\nDaily office employment\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://charmeck.org/city/charlotte/Airport/Pages/default.aspx\" target=\"_blank\">Airport</a>\r\n\r\nDemographics\r\n\r\nArea businesses\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.ncagr.gov/markets/facilities/markets/charlotte/\" target=\"_blank\">Farmers market</a>\r\n\r\nCity Park association\r\n\r\nAmenities\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Why City Park', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '73-revision-6', '', '', '2013-04-26 19:21:54', '2013-04-26 19:21:54', '', '73', 'http://smileg.com